Brian

Brian

I just saw you listened to a track, so I pulled it up in spotify too.
Ah. I don't see it. I'm not liking how these updates are invisible to me. Oh well.

Brian

Brian
I am good
just here at work
how are you?

Is there a club there that plays it? I am working too, the same mundane job, but I decided I want to go back to school, probably just SCC or PVCC for some classes.

Brian
yeah, I should go back to school too

Mt Eden this Thursday
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oIEEIif21g4

Brian
I meet my friend Ryan there.
Sweet vibes man.

Hey. Why weren't we friends? 
What's up?

Brian
I'm inviting everyone to Chelsea's reunion because she was my favorite chearleader.
What's up with you?

I joined that group for the reunion. I don't think I am going.
I'm just a work, ready for my three day weekend.

Brian
I think I am going as a pimp with 3 girls, my wife and two roommates.

How's the married life?
And dogs?

Brian
Married life is really good.  The dogs are little stinkers.  We had puppies and sold them all.  Iga is constantly doing some fun art project around the house so it's become really beautiful here.  You should come by sometime.
I heard you got a mustang.  Are you still living on Buteo?  I wish I had living with my parents longer so save up, we have almost no savings and I sold my 370Z from my dad and spent all that money too.

I'm living in Tempe, been here for two and a half years. That's about how old my car is.
I don't save money either. Just pay bills and that's about it.

Brian
I just bought a giant sculpture from this guy: https://www.facebook.com/brian.korsedal and I assembled it in my back yard for my bird to live in.
Brian Korsedal

Brian
Its like when you get married every challenge becomes half as hard.
Teamwork.
Hey. Do you still smoke and or do any drugs?

Brian
I smoke pretty regularly.  Why?
Just had an IPA at the Chymist last night.  Alcohol is a drug.
We ate so much.

Brian
Avoiding the other stuff since I got married.  Acquiring it is no problem though, I know tons of people that do it regularly and go to raves.  There are tons of coke heads in this city especially.
I just wanted pot and mdma for Las Vegas. Leaving here in a little bit, though.

Brian
Hmm, need a few days notice, not sure if these guys will talk about it over instant message.
Don't worry about it.

Brian
Easily get you the weed, want to come over later?

Thanks though. I do not need anything
I am leaving in two hours
I am leaving in two hours

Brian
Oh dang, I am at my boss' house until 5 ish
It was just a last minute thought. Should have asked sooner.

Brian
Well thank you for thinking of me 
Going to EDC?
Yep. Have you been before?

Brian
I went in 2011 with Tiesto and Borgore and Avicci
Iga went too but we didn't meet yet, pretty crazy.
I am excited to see the rave kids

Brian
Yeah good fun
I'm sure they will have drugs, but it's going to be hot.
